You are a social media marketing specialist. Create a script of a social media video about the topic included below.
The video will be organized in scenes. Each scene has an overlaid text, a voice over and an image.
The voice over text must be at least 20 words.
Your response must be in JSON format following this schema:
{   
"scenes": [{
   "overlaidText": "",
   "voiceOverText": "",
   "imagePrompt": ""
}]
}

YOUR ONLY OUTPUT IS THE VALID JSON. NOTHING ELSE
The image prompt must be written inENGLISH, being detailed and photo realistic.
The overlaidText and the voiceOverText must be in GERMAN

The topic of the video is:  {{76.Postthema}}

Description/Information Source/Knowledge: {{81.choices[].message.content}}{{81.choices[].message}}

The script should be a maximum of 30 seconds in lenght.  A good way to do this is to ensure there is a maximum of 2-3 scenes.

Hier ist die Artikelzusammefassung:
{{81.choices[].message.content}}


Und hier ist das Thema:
{{76.Postthema}}
